  section.se__ingredients
    .container
      .section__intro
        h2 Main ingredients
          svg.decor: use(xlink:href="#decor")
        p What is inside Simpleat?
      .ingredients
        .ingredients--item
          .img: img(src="img/ingredients1.png", alt="")
          .text
            h3 Soybean protein
            p Soy is a complete protein and rich in vitamins and minerals. Soybean protein provides all the essential amino acids in the amounts needed for human health.
        .ingredients--item
          .img: img(src="img/ingredients2.png", alt="")
          .text
            h3 Oils
            p The perfect mix of lipids from sea algae, coconut, sunflower, flaxseed and canola. Rich with omega-3, unsaturated fatty acids DHA and EPA, which contribute to the normal function of the heart and brain function.
        .ingredients--item
          .img: img(src="img/ingredients3.png", alt="")
          .text
            h3 Oat flour
            p Oat flour is made from whole oats and contains beta-glucans. This fiber have shown to lower risk factors for heart disease such as high cholesterol and high blood pressure.
        .ingredients--item
          .img: img(src="img/ingredients4.png", alt="")
          .text
            h3 Isomaltulose
            p Isomaltulose is a natural occurring disaccharide. It keeps you energetic without the spikes of refined sugar.
        .ingredients--item
          .img: img(src="img/ingredients5.png", alt="")
          .text
            h3 Minerals & Vitamins
            p A bottle of Simpleat contains 20% of daily requirements of all micronutrients for your body.
